{"article_id":"ol568cTY7A3Nq9a5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump responded to criticism from former Defense Secretary James Mattis","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"by calling him an \" overrated \" military leader","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"whom he relished firing .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"\" Probably the only thing","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Barack Obama and I have in common","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"is that we both had the honor","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"of firing Jim Mattis , the world ' s most overrated General , \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Trump tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" I asked for his letter of resignation ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"& felt great about . \"","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Mr. Mattis , a retired four-star Marine general","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"whom the president previously called a hero ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"criticized the president Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"for \" militarizing \" the federal response to nationwide protests over police brutality .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"He called Mr. Trump \" the first president in my lifetime","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"who does not try to unite the American people","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"- does not even pretend to try . \"","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"He served two years as Defense secretary","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"before leaving in January 2019 .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"The president said of Mr. Mattis ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"\" His nickname was ' Chaos ' ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"which I didn ' t like ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"& changed it to ' Mad Dog ' .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"His primary strength was not military , but rather personal public relations . \"","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"In fact , Mr. Mattis was given the nickname \" Mad Dog \" in the military","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"long before Mr. Trump was elected .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"A San Diego Tribune article in 2013 refers to the nickname ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that Mr. Mattis didn ' t like the moniker .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Said the president ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" I gave him a new life , things","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"to do ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"and battles","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"to win ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"but he seldom ' brought home the bacon ' .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"I didn ' t like his ' leadership ' style or much else about him ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and many others agree .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Glad he is gone ! \"","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Mr. Mattis wasn ' t fired ;","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"he resigned","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"after clashing with the president over the administration ' s policy in Syria .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"White House press secretary Kayleigh McEnany also weighed in ,","depth":2},{"id":42,"text":"saying","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Mattis ' s statement was \" little more than a self-promotional stunt","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"to appease the DC elite . \"","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"She tweeted","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"Mr. Trump \" is the law and order President","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"that has restored peace to our nation ' s streets . \"","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"\" Mattis ' small words pale in comparison to @ POTUS ' strong action , \"","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"she said .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":99,"left":90,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":68,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":59,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":52,"right":58,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":0,"right":51,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":51,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"elabora